<SYNC START=1317554><P CLASS=KRCC>쓰러뜨린다!
<SYNC START=1318432><P CLASS=KRCC>그리고!
<SYNC START=1319376><P CLASS=KRCC>붙잡힌 사람들을!
<SYNC START=1320725><P CLASS=KRCC>해방시키는거다!
<SYNC START=1322830><P CLASS=KRCC>돌입한다!
<SYNC START=1324685><P CLASS=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=1335343><P CLASS=KRCC>왔구나 고라이온!
<SYNC START=1337981><P CLASS=KRCC>&nbsp;
